Five men stand accused of murdering former Bafana Bafana and Orlando Pirates goalkeeper Senzo Meyiwa.   PRETORIA - The Senzo Meyiwa murder matter is back at the North Gauteng High Court. Meyiwa, the former Bafana Bafana goalkeeper and captain, was gunned down almost eight-years ago at the home of his girlfriend, Kelly Khumalo in Vosloorus.